00:07:59,587 --> 00:08:01,250
Bagaimana kamu bisa tahu
tentang Park Jun-seo?

114
00:08:03,545 --> 00:08:04,425
Park Jun-seo?

115
00:08:06,678 --> 00:08:08,325
Ya, benar.

116
00:08:10,027 --> 00:08:13,531
Tentu saja kamu pasti marah.

117
00:08:14,261 --> 00:08:16,171
Jadi kamu ingin balas dendam padaku?

